description.p:
(1) A solid oxide fuel cell containing a fuel electrode which comprises vanadium carbide;


(2) The fuel cell as stated in above (1), wherein vanadium carbide and a carbon-series fuel are used in the fuel electrode;


(3) The fuel cell as stated in above (2), wherein natural gas or naphtha is reformed;


(4) The fuel cell as stated in above (2), wherein the carbon-series fuel is coal and the partial oxidation reaction of the gasification reaction of the coal generates power; and


(5) A fuel electrode for a solid oxide fuel cell, which comprises vanadium carbide.
